(f), no special allowance is paid for any period for which the interest rate determined under 682.202(a)(2)(iv)(A)
for that loan does not exceed_

(i) 12 percent in the case of a Federal SLS or PLUS loan made prior to October 1, 1992;

(ii) 11 percent in the case of a Federal SLS loan made on or after October 1, 1992; or






